      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">and <math display=\"inline\">\\hat{F}_X(s) = \\int_0^\\infty e^{-sx} dF_X(x)</math> is the Laplace–Stieltjes transform of <math display=\"inline\">F_X</math>.</p>",
